==Trivia==
*Red dragons formerly inhabited the Red Dragon Isle (now [[Lava Dragon Isle]]) in the [[Wilderness]], but they were replaced with [[Lava dragon]]s in the [[Wilderness Rejuvenation]] update (in canon, this transformation was due to the fact that they had been living surrounded by lava for a very long time).
*Red dragons are the rarest type of chromatic dragon.

